
public class ForLoop1 {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub
		
		String[] values = new String[5];
		values[0] = "Zero";
		values[1] = "One";
		values[2] = "Two";
		values[3] = "Three";
		values[4] = "Four";
		
		
		for (String value : values) {
			System.out.println(value);
			
		}

	}

}
